{"tid":1057814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【出席飯局】被富商逼喝酒兼喪鬧 葉璇：應列為圖謀不軌性侵的一種","createTime":"2019-03-12T06:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T05:35:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dae19b48220a41e747ec71ad19d7e05476e39aad","tid":1057814,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T06:42:22.000Z","msg":"葉璇近日是非一籮籮，早前涉對前男友小默先生舊愛呂梅造成名譽權侵害，必須公開道歉，且交罰款8萬元人民幣，她在道歉信上稱當初真是腦子壞掉了(新聞連結： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2F4New2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2F4New2&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Dv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=dd351961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2F4New2</a> )，對此事感到特別後悔。<br />\n今日大陸傳媒指葉璇日前出席飯局，疑被富商強迫喝酒，葉璇亦在微博回應遭富商喪鬧一小時的過程，留言：「有沒有人像我今天一樣，在一桌領導面前被一個國營商場董事長逼喝酒一個小時後，客客氣氣說不喝酒，仍然繼續逼我喝，還開罵，但我仍然不喝，飯也不吃站起來就走了的？我是不是以後再也不能去逛這個商場了。」<br />\n有網民質疑：「沒有利益，叫你去跟一群陌生人吃飯會去嗎，我關心的是誰喊你去的？」葉璇坦言：「我同學請客，沒利益。只有你這種人才會吃個飯都要講利益。」<br />\n不少網民都認為該富商圖謀不軌，叫葉璇小心一些，原來此次聚餐是由葉璇的同學請客，席間還有一名大陸公安目睹事發經過，他挺身而出，責罵該富商，葉璇認為富商逼人飲酒，行為可恥，並非「勸酒」，葉璇留言回覆網民時罵富商是「人渣」，又指逼人喝酒應該列為圖謀不軌性侵的一種，她稱該富商口出惡言罵人，女人不能對這種惡勢力就範，用喪失尊嚴換來的任何東西只會讓自己終身作嘔，又指沒有專業實力做事的人，才靠喝酒拿業務，真正有才華的人，根本不屑走潛規則得到機會。<br />\n葉璇近年一向語出驚人的，近年主力北上發展，日前有fans跟她談及趙麗穎産子一事，葉璇忽然回應：「「早就生完了啊！」即被傳秘密産子，要經理人出來平息風波。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190312/large/1552361185_4961.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190312%2Flarge%2F1552361185_4961.jpg&h=279cc869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190312/59358881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59358881&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6Dv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ef0c2b8e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F59358881&h=a64b0053\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190312/59358881</a>"},{"pid":"f43b2ff8d6068b37dacb0ab2a7c41a997354bb1d","tid":1057814,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T06:50:36.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"7307ae081cd14e687b0f40d311cbf281280f2f7e","tid":1057814,"uid":175865,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"咁妳又出席，扮乜撚嘢上菜吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3703f3d6735c0cd11422f53ed14737577d88e1ed","tid":1057814,"uid":160964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:20:46.000Z","msg":"港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db84446c0f71ebd6fcb068fcb41ecd9bc5264542","tid":1057814,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5914c8fbdc40f4cedc074b4d6984076c909a0d5","tid":1057814,"uid":48905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"db84446c0f71ebd6fcb068fcb41ecd9bc5264542","tid":1057814,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:33:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nB6pQR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nB6pQR.png&h=6ba7ccd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e88cee0e1bbbd30481d978b397413e0a408afb25","tid":1057814,"uid":43061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"佢屋企唔係都有錢架咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢真係似唔洗陪酒WO"},{"pid":"8e023b7d944d758e23a418c567249bd5c029dca3","tid":1057814,"uid":63870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07